                <componentInstanceProperties>
                    <name>richTextValue</name>
                    <value>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Hi {{{Recipient.FirstName}}},&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;It has been a pleasure to be a part of your 10X Health Care Team!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;I&amp;#39;d like to introduce you to my colleague, Jillian Banayan.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Jillian is your Wellness Concierge. Her responsibility is to handhold you on your journey to optimal health! Jillian will be your point of contact moving forward to ensure we set you up for success along the way!&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;Here&amp;#39;s a little more about your Concierge:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Jillian is a Certified Holistic Nutrition Coach, AADP Board Certified Holistic Health Practitioner, and certified yoga instructor with over 8 years of experience in the health and wellness industry. With a focus on preventative health and functional nutrition, Jillian integrates evidence-based protocols that combine personalized nutrition plans and behavior-based coaching to help clients achieve their long-term health goals.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Passionate about hormone optimization, gut health, and increasing longevity, Jillian works closely with patients to create actionable plans that promote sustainable wellness.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Jillian, {{{Recipient.FirstName}}} shared some of the top wellness goals below:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;INSERT GOALS&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;INSERT GOALS&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;INSERT GOALS&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;{{{Recipient.FirstName}}}, Jillian is fully prepared to provide you with the support you need to 10X your health through monthly check ins, answering questions, and keeping you on track with your protocol!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Your first meeting with Jillian will be on &lt;strong&gt;[Date &amp;amp; Time]&lt;/strong&gt;. Keep an eye out for a calendar invite and reminders coming your way! Jillian will connect with you to go over your next steps: completing an inventory check, walking you through your protocol, and ensuring you feel fully confident with your medications when they arrive.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Heads up&lt;/b&gt;: If anything&amp;nbsp;is lost, missing, or damaged, please let us know within 24 hours and send a quick photo.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;In the meantime, if you have any questions or need to reschedule your call with Jillian, please don&amp;#39;t hesitate to reply to this email or click on the scheduling link.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://&quot;&gt;https://calendly.com/jbanayan/precision-wellness-protocol-welcome-inventory-check&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;In the meantime, if you have any questions, please don&amp;#39;t hesitate to reply to this email or give us a call.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;You can contact Jillian directly via email at &lt;a href=&quot;https://&quot;&gt;jbanayan@10xhealthsystem.com&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;In Health,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Your 10X Care Team&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</value>
